oda-data-set.name: cr_modification_total
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total from enrollment_notification_log enl left join front_end_partner fep on fep.cbs_acct_code =enl.esa_code left join fep_device_mapping fdm on fep.pk = fdm.front_end_partner_fk left join device_tag_request d on d.requested_device_id =fdm.device_id left join device_tag_request_ext dte on dte.pk =d.pk where notification_mode ='PRODUCTION' and enl.device_id in (select distinct er.device_id from enrollment_ref er join node on node.enrollment_ref = er.id where lower(certification_status) ='certified' and node.active='1' ) and date_trunc('day',enl.create_date) =(current_date-1) and enrollment_types='cr-modification'

oda-data-set.name: cr_new
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and enrollment_type='cr-new'

oda-data-set.name: er_new_total
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and enrollment_type='er-new'

oda-data-set.name: hourly_enrollment
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total,enrollment_type ,extract(hour from cal.last_modified) from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and enrollment_type not like '%modification%' group by enrollment_type,extract(hour from cal.last_modified) order by extract(hour from cal.last_modified)

oda-data-set.name: enrollment_breakdown
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total,enrollment_type from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and enrollment_type not like '%modification%' group by enrollment_type

oda-data-set.name: capture_duration
oda-data-set.xml-property: SELECT substr(ref_device_id,1,strpos(ref_device_id,'-')-1) as device_type,current_date, date_trunc('day',ACTIVITY_START_TIME) as Date_,activity, round(cast((avg(duration/60000)) as numeric),2) as average_duration_minutes from client_activity_log where ACTIVITY in ('PORTRAIT_CAPTURE','FINGERPRINT') and date_trunc('day',ACTIVITY_START_TIME)=(current_date-1) GROUP BY substr(ref_device_id,1,strpos(ref_device_id,'-')-1),date_trunc('day',ACTIVITY_START_TIME),activity ORDER BY date_trunc('day',ACTIVITY_START_TIME) desc

oda-data-set.name: device_enrollment_time
oda-data-set.xml-property: SELECT substr(ref_device_id,1,strpos(ref_device_id,'-')-1) as device_type, round(cast((avg(duration/60000)) as numeric),2) as average_duration_minutes from client_activity_log where ACTIVITY ='END_TO_END_CAPTURE' and date_trunc('day',ACTIVITY_START_TIME)=(current_date-1) GROUP BY substr(ref_device_id,1,strpos(ref_device_id,'-')-1),date_trunc('day',ACTIVITY_START_TIME) ORDER BY date_trunc('day',ACTIVITY_START_TIME) desc

oda-data-set.name: hourly_status_trend
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total,sync_status ,extract(hour from cal.last_modified) from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) group by sync_status,extract(hour from cal.last_modified) order by extract(hour from cal.last_modified)

oda-data-set.name: status_data
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total,sync_status from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and enrollment_type not like '%modification%' group by sync_status

oda-data-set.name: sync_confirmed
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and sync_status='SYNC_CONFIRMED' and enrollment_type not like '%modification%'

oda-data-set.name: sync_failed_validation
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and sync_status='SYNC_FAILED_VALIDATION' and enrollment_type not like '%odification%'

oda-data-set.name: sync_pending_confirmation
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and sync_status='SYNC_PENDING_CONFIRMATION' and enrollment_type not like '%modification%'

oda-data-set.name: cr_new_by_status
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total,sync_status ,extract(hour from cal.last_modified),cale.enrollment_type from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and enrollment_type='cr-new' group by sync_status,extract(hour from cal.last_modified),cale.enrollment_type order by extract(hour from cal.last_modified)

oda-data-set.name: cr_new_pie_chart
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total,sync_status from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and enrollment_type='cr-new' and enrollment_type not like '%modification%' group by sync_status

oda-data-set.name: er_piechart
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total,sync_status from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and enrollment_type='er-new' group by sync_status

oda-data-set.name: er_by_status
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(*) as total,sync_status ,extract(hour from cal.last_modified),cale.enrollment_type from client_activity_log_ext cale left join client_activity_log cal on cale.pk=cal.pk where date_trunc('day',cal.last_modified) = (current_date-1) and enrollment_type='er-new' group by sync_status,extract(hour from cal.last_modified),cale.enrollment_type order by extract(hour from cal.last_modified)

oda-data-set.name: total_attempts
oda-data-set.xml-property: select substr(ref_device_id,1,strpos(ref_device_id,'-')-1),count(*) as total_attempts from nimc_sync_log nsl where date_trunc('day',create_date) = (current_date-1) and reg_type not like '%Modification%' GROUP BY substr(ref_device_id,1,strpos(ref_device_id,'-')-1)

oda-data-set.name: attempts
oda-data-set.xml-property: select round(avg(attempts)),substr(ref_device_id,1,strpos(ref_device_id,'-')-1),activity from ( select count(unique_activity_code) as attempts ,unique_activity_code ,cal.activity,realtime_device_id as ref_device_id from client_activity_log cal where date_trunc('day',cal.activity_start_time )=(current_date-1) and activity in ('PORTRAIT_CAPTURE','FINGERPRINT') group by unique_activity_code ,realtime_device_id,cal.activity) a group by substr(ref_device_id,1,strpos(ref_device_id,'-')-1),activity
